Distribution. Found in the western portion of the Northern Deserts region: from approximately Fitzroy Crossing, Western Australia , to west of Daly Waters, Northern Territory (
Fig. 2
). Ecological niche modeling suggests that the sandstone escarpments of the Top End biogeographic region represent the northern barrier to this species, and that the southern barrier (~ 18 °S) is the approximate transition to extreme aridity and highly variable rainfall (
Catullo et al. 2013
).
